            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". It was the title which Christ most frequently applied to himself; and there are but two instances in which it is applied to him by another, viz., by Stephen (",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Acts 7:56",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ") and by John (",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Revelation 1:13",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
