            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " :); and when acquiescing in the title \"Son of God,\" addressed to himself, he sometimes immediately after substitutes \"Son of Man\" (",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "John 1:50",
            "children": []
          },
          {
